'''飓风艾米莉'''（{{lang-en|Hurricane Emily}}）是活跃度低于平均水平的[[1987年大西洋飓风季|1987年大西洋飓风季]]形成的唯一一场[[热带气旋等级|大型飓风]]，源自9月20日离开非洲西海岸的[[东风波|东风波]]。气旋很快就达到飓风强度，然后[[快速增强|快速增强]]。9月22日，风暴达到[[最大持续风速|持续风速]]每小时205公里，最低[[气压|气压]]958[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，28.29[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]）的最高强度。接下来气旋略有减弱，强度回落至[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]下的二级飓风标准并[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]][[多米尼加|多米尼加共和国]]。降级成热带风暴后，艾米莉快速朝东北方向穿越大西洋，在此期间进入第二轮快速增强期，再于9月25日直接从[[百慕大|百慕大]]上空经过。次日，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]发布针对飓风的最后一份公告，宣布风暴转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]。

飓风艾米莉于9月21日在[[向风群岛|向风群岛]]产生狂风暴雨，导致大量民宅受损，香蕉产业遭受重创，向风群岛的损失总额约为29万1000美元。风暴袭击多米尼加共和国时虽然强度很高，但当地遭受的破坏程度只达到中等水平，共有三人丧生，经济损失约为3000万美元。气旋之后出人意料地快速强化，对百慕大构成重大打击，导致价值5000万美元的破坏，还令16人受伤。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Emily 1987 track.png}}
飓风艾米莉源自9月13日离开非洲西南岸的[[东风波|东风波]]，这股东风波同[[热带辐合带|热带辐合带]]关联，在低[[纬度|纬度]]洋面向西移动。天气系统的组织结构很不稳定，其中的深层[[对流|对流]]和[[外流_(气象学)|外流]]在连续几天里虽有发展，但又经常减弱，一直不成气候。到了9月18日，这片[[热带扰动|热带扰动]]进入存在下沉气流的海域，这种情况不利于[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]发展。两天后，天气系统同热带辐合带分离，并且很快就在[[巴巴多斯|巴巴多斯]]东南方向975公里洋面发展成这年大西洋飓风季的第十二号热带低气压。<ref name="PG1">{{cite report | author = Harold P. Gerrish | publisher = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | date = 1987-11-12 | accessdate = 2016-10-05 | title = Hurricane Emily Preliminary Report: Page One | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303175946/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1987-prelim/emily/prelim01.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1987-prelim/emily/prelim01.gif | format = [[GIF|GIF]] | archivedate = 2016-03-03 }}</ref>

9月20日，气旋逐渐增强，于[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]下午18点达到热带风暴标准并获名“艾米莉”（{{lang|en|Emily}}）。风暴围绕强烈[[亚热带气旋|副热带]][[高压脊|高压脊]]的边缘总体朝[[罗盘方位|西北偏西]]方向移动，其中心到{{lang|en|UTC}}9月21日中午12点时已直接从[[圣文森特岛|圣文森特岛]]上空经过，风暴此时的风速为每小时85公里。<ref name="PG1" />受上方的[[反气旋|反气旋]]影响，艾米莉在快速朝[[伊斯帕尼奥拉岛|伊斯帕尼奥拉岛]]逼近的同时[[快速增强|快速增强]]。从{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}9月21日下午18点至9月22日下午18点的24小时里，风暴中心气压降至958[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，28.29[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]），降幅达44毫巴（百帕），风速也提升到每小时205公里，在[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]下已接近三级飓风强度上限，艾米莉至此成为[[1987年大西洋飓风季|1987年大西洋飓风季]]唯一的[[热带气旋等级|大型飓风]]。<ref name="PG2">{{cite report | author = Harold P. Gerrish | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1987-11-12 | accessdate = 2016-10-05 | title = Hurricane Emily Preliminary Report: Page Two | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | deadurl = no | format = GIF | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002022349/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1987-prelim/emily/prelim02.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1987-prelim/emily/prelim02.gif }}</ref>[[飓风猎人|飓风猎人]]侦察机在艾米莉达到最高强度时测得的飞行高度层风速达每小时250公里，气压低至949毫巴（百帕，28.02英寸汞柱），但这项气压数值没有得到正式确认<ref name="PG19">{{cite report | author = Harold P. Gerrish | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1987-11-12 | accessdate = 2016-10-05 | title = Hurricane Emily Preliminary Report: Page Nineteen | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1987-prelim/emily/prelim19.gif | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303215626/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1987-prelim/emily/prelim19.gif | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | format = GIF }}</ref><ref name="PG20">{{cite report | author = Harold P. Gerrish | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1987-11-12 | accessdate = 2016-10-05 | title = Hurricane Emily Preliminary Report: Page Twenty | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | format = GIF | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303232229/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1987-prelim/emily/prelim20.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1987-prelim/emily/prelim20.gif }}</ref>。

[[File:Eye_of_Hurricane_Emily_1987.jpg|200px]]拍下艾米莉[[风眼|风眼]]的照片]]

9月22日晚至9月23日清晨，飓风在[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]前略有减弱。{{lang|en|UTC}}凌晨3点左右，艾米莉的[[风眼|风眼]]从[[巴拉奥纳|巴拉奥纳]]和[[巴尼|巴尼]]之间上岸，气旋此时的风速仍达每小时175公里。登陆不到12小时后，飓风已降级成热带风暴，以风力时速100公里强度从[[海地|海地]]附近进入大西洋。受几乎没有移动的[[锋_(气象)|锋面天气系统]]影响，气旋在行经[[巴哈马|巴哈马]]东部期间大幅减弱。艾米莉总体保持北上趋势，环流中心于9月24日从距[[伊纳瓜岛|伊纳瓜岛]]和[[马亚瓜纳岛|马亚瓜纳岛]]非常近的位置掠过。<ref name="PG2" />

9月24日中午，艾米莉已嵌入中纬度[[西风带|西风带]]并快速朝东北移动。[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]预计风暴会同东北方向的锋面天气系统融合，进而在24小时内转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]。但是，艾米莉实际上却出人意料地在9月25日进入第二轮快速增强期，强化速度一度达到爆发增强标准，中心气压每小时降幅达2.5毫巴。到了{{lang|en|UTC}}早上6点，风暴已再度达到飓风标准，其中心于{{lang|en|UTC}}11点45分直接从[[百慕大|百慕大]]上空经过，此时风速达到每小时140公里。不久后，气旋达到第二波强度高峰，风力时速达到150公里，最低气压974毫巴（百帕，28.76英寸汞柱）。<ref name="PG2" />

9月25日，艾米莉继续朝东北方向前进，移动速度还在不断提升，于当晚达到每小时85公里。风暴开始转变成温带气旋，前进速度达到每小时100公里峰值，这样高的移动速度在有纪录以来所有热带气旋中也可以排到第三位。飓风同[[锋_(气象)|斜压区]]相互影响，于{{lang|en|UTC}}9月26日下午18点完全转变成温带气旋，气象机构随即发布最后一份公告。<ref name="PG3">{{cite report | author = Harold P. Gerrish | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1987-11-12 | accessdate = 2016-10-05 | title = Hurricane Emily Preliminary Report: Page Three | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303210815/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1987-prelim/emily/prelim03.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1987-prelim/emily/prelim03.gif | deadurl = no | format = GIF }}</ref>

== 防灾措施 ==
[[File:Hurricane_Emily_(1987)_near_Bermuda.JPG|thumb]]
9月21日热带风暴艾米莉快速逼近[[向风群岛|向风群岛]]时，[[格林纳达|格林纳达]]、[[巴巴多斯|巴巴多斯]]、[[圣文森特岛|圣文森特岛]]和[[圣卢西亚|圣卢西亚]]收到[[热带气旋警告|热带风暴警告]]，[[马提尼克|马提尼克]]接获[[热带气旋警告|热带风暴观察预警]]<ref name="PG9">{{cite report | author = Harold P. Gerrish | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1987-11-12 | accessdate = 2016-10-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303183612/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1987-prelim/emily/prelim09.gif | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | format = GIF | title = Hurricane Emily Preliminary Report: Page Nine | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1987-prelim/emily/prelim09.gif }}</ref>。风暴经过这些岛屿后<ref name="PG1" />，上述观察预警和警告都在当晚中止<ref name="PG9" />。9月22日清晨，[[多米尼加|多米尼加共和国]]南部沿海地区、[[海地|海地]]南部和国西南半岛进入[[热带气旋警告|飓风警告]]生效状态<ref name="PG9" />。艾米莉达到大型飓风标准后，气象部门预计气旋登陆时仍会有飓风强度，所以向海地北部发布飓风警告。当晚，[[巴哈马|巴哈马]]东南部和[[特克斯和凯科斯群岛|特克斯和凯科斯群岛]]收到[[热带气旋警告|飓风观察预警]]。气象机构预计风暴会在巴哈马上空重新增强后，飓风观察预警又升级成飓风警告。<ref name="PG10">{{cite report | author = Harold P. Gerrish | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1987-11-12 | accessdate = 2016-10-05 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303232853/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1987-prelim/emily/prelim10.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1987-prelim/emily/prelim10.gif | title = Hurricane Emily Preliminary Report: Page Ten | deadurl = no | format = GIF }}</ref>

美国国家飓风中心预计艾米莉9月23日的移动路线会更朝西侧偏移<ref name="PG2" />，所以向巴哈马西北部发出飓风观察预警，之后又升级成飓风警告，并向[[古巴|古巴]]东部发布飓风警告。9月24日清晨，由于艾米莉已进入大西洋上空，加勒比群岛及巴哈马的所有观察预警和警告全部中止。<ref name="PG2" /><ref name="PG10" />9月25日，[[百慕大|百慕大]]收到特别公告，称该岛很可能会受到热带风暴强度大风影响<ref name="PG10" />。随着气旋出人意料地大幅增强<ref name="PG2" />，百慕大又收到另一份特别公告，称该岛可能会在9月25日受到飓风强度狂风袭击。风暴当晚经过该国后，上述公告停止生效。<ref name="PG10" />

向风群岛各地的学校和企业在风暴逼近前关闭<ref name="TFLS1">{{cite news | agency = [[美联社|Associated Press]] | newspaper = The Free-Lance Star | date = 1987-09-22 | accessdate = 2016-10-05 | title = Hurricane Emily strengthening | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=CONLAAAAIBAJ&sjid=vIsDAAAAIBAJ&dq=hurricane-emily-strengthening&pg=1166%2C1809291 | archive-date = 2022-02-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220219015820/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=CONLAAAAIBAJ&sjid=vIsDAAAAIBAJ&dq=hurricane-emily-strengthening&pg=1166%2C1809291 }}</ref>。多米尼加共和国首都[[圣多明哥|圣多明哥]]约有6000人在气旋来袭前撤离<ref>{{cite news | agency = Associated Press | newspaper = Pittsburgh Post-Gazette | date = 1987-09-24 | accessdate = 2016-10-05 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=CgQOAAAAIBAJ&sjid=1m0DAAAAIBAJ&pg=4735,8578971&dq=hurricane+emily | title = Hurricane Emily kills 3 in Caribbean | archive-date = 2022-02-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220219015840/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=CgQOAAAAIBAJ&sjid=1m0DAAAAIBAJ&pg=4735%2C8578971&dq=hurricane+emily }}</ref>。虽然艾米莉自始至终没有朝[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]]逼近，但该州官员还是建议居民严加防范<ref>{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | newspaper = Miami Herald | date = 1987-09-23 | accessdate = 2016-10-05 | title = County yawns at Hurricane Emily; Officials prepare for possible disaster | url = http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=MH&s_site=miami&p_multi=MH&p_theme=realcities&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=0EB36805F2C14848&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date:D&s_trackval=GooglePM | archive-date = 2020-12-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201213073705/http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=MH&s_site=miami&p_multi=MH&p_theme=realcities&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=0EB36805F2C14848&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date%3AD&s_trackval=GooglePM | dead-url = no }}</ref>。政府官员探讨艾米莉袭击该州的可能，对飓风保持警惕<ref>{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | newspaper = Miami Herald | date = 1987-09-23 | accessdate = 2016-10-05 | title = Emily brings hurricanes to mind | url = http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=MH&s_site=miami&p_multi=MH&p_theme=realcities&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=0EB36805E96F0057&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date:D&s_trackval=GooglePM | archive-date = 2020-12-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201213073711/http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=MH&s_site=miami&p_multi=MH&p_theme=realcities&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=0EB36805E96F0057&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date%3AD&s_trackval=GooglePM | dead-url = no }}</ref>。特克斯和凯科斯群岛居民从低洼地区疏散到各个岛屿上的避难所<ref>{{cite news | author = A. J. Dickerson | newspaper = The Free-Lance Star | date = 1987-09-24 | accessdate = 2016-10-05 | title = Hurricane warning lifted as Emily weakens | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=IHsQAAAAIBAJ&sjid=vIsDAAAAIBAJ&pg=1148,1449306&dq=emily+evacuations | archive-date = 2022-02-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220219021700/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=IHsQAAAAIBAJ&sjid=vIsDAAAAIBAJ&pg=1148%2C1449306&dq=emily+evacuations }}</ref>。

9月25日，随着艾米莉逼近加拿大近海水域，成立尚不足一个月的[[加拿大飓风中心|加拿大飓风中心]]首次针对热带气旋发布公告，称[[纽芬兰岛|纽芬兰岛]]东南方向海域有可能出现狂风暴雨<ref>{{cite report | author = Canadian Hurricane Centre | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160818074707/http://www.ec.gc.ca/ouragans-hurricanes/default.asp?lang=En&n=140D452D-1 | date = 2009-07-15 | url = http://www.ec.gc.ca/ouragans-hurricanes/default.asp?lang=En&n=140D452D-1 | title = History of the Canadian Hurricane Centre (CHC) | publisher = [[加拿大环境部|Environment and Climate Change Canada]] | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2016-10-05 | archivedate = 2016-08-18 }}</ref><ref>{{cite report | author = RWH | publisher = Canadian Hurricane Centre | date = 1987-09-25 | title = Canadian Hurricane Prognostic Message Issued By Environment Canada at 0830 PM ADT Friday 25 September 1987 | accessdate = 2016-10-05 | format = [[文本文件|TXT]] | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160807073453/http://www2.ec.gc.ca/ouragans-hurricanes/140D452D-5A08-43B0-A9FF-9B9B4B8C033E/187firstbulletinhurricane-emily_e-rev.txt | archivedate = 2016-08-07 | url = http://www.ec.gc.ca/ouragans-hurricanes/140D452D-5A08-43B0-A9FF-9B9B4B8C033E/187firstbulletinhurricane-emily_e-rev.txt }}</ref>。

== 影响和善后 ==
[[File:Emily_1987_rainfall.png|thumb]]的降水分布]]

艾米莉以热带风暴强度经过[[小安的列斯群岛|小安的列斯群岛]]，在多个岛上降下暴雨。巴巴多斯因狂风导致大范围地区的房屋屋顶受损，还有许多树木倒塌，输电线缆中断，岛上经济损失达到十万美元<ref name="TFLS1" /><ref name="MWR" />。[[圣文森特岛|圣文森特岛]]的香蕉产业受到重创，约有70%的作物被毁<ref name="MWR" /><ref>{{cite web | author = Department of Public Affairs | publisher = United States Department of State | date = 1994-11 | accessdate = 2016-10-05 | title = St. Vincent and the Grenadines | url = http://dosfan.lib.uic.edu/ERC/bgnotes/wha/saintvincent9411.html | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303170512/http://dosfan.lib.uic.edu/ERC/bgnotes/wha/saintvincent9411.html | archivedate = 2016-03-03 }}</ref>。全岛各地的学校在气旋来袭前关闭<ref>{{cite news | agency = Associated Press | newspaper = [[纽约时报|The New York Times]] | date = 1987-09-22 | accessdate = 2016-10-05 | title = Hurricane Emily Strengthens, Posing Threat to Hispaniola | publisher = The New York Times Company | archivedate = 2016-02-17 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160217060911/http://www.nytimes.com/1987/09/22/us/hurricane-emily-strengthens-posing-threat-to-hispaniola.html | url = http://www.nytimes.com/1987/09/22/us/hurricane-emily-strengthens-posing-threat-to-hispaniola.html }}</ref>，岛上在六小时内就降下76毫米雨量<ref name="MWR">{{cite report | author1 = Robert A. Case | author2 = Harold P. Gerrish | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1988-04 | accessdate = 2016-10-05 | title = Atlantic Hurricane Season of 1987 | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/general/lib/lib1/nhclib/mwreviews/1987.pdf | format = [[便携式文档格式|PDF]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304040405/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/general/lib/lib1/nhclib/mwreviews/1987.pdf | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>，导致洪水泛滥，八户居民被迫离开家园<ref name="TFLS1" />，该岛的损失总额约为19万1000美元，其中大部分是因[[山崩|山体滑坡]]所致<ref>{{cite web | author = Nicholas DeGraff | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160309094028/http://isis.uwimona.edu.jm/uds/Land_St_Lucia.html | publisher = University of California, Santa Cruz | date = 1999-08-25 | accessdate = 2016-10-05 | title = Natural Hazards and Disasters: Landslides in St. Lucia | url = http://isis.uwimona.edu.jm/uds/Land_St_Lucia.html | archivedate = 2016-03-09 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。艾米莉的外围[[雨带|雨带]]令[[波多黎各|波多黎各]]西南部普降中雨，最高降雨量有118毫米<ref>{{cite report | author = David M. Roth | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | year = 2009 | accessdate = 2016-10-05 | title = Hurricane Emily - September 21–23, 1987 | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain//emily1987.html | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304060007/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain//emily1987.html | deadurl = no | date =  }}</ref>。

飓风在多米尼加共和国降下暴雨，引发大面积[[泥石流|泥石流]]并夺走两条人命<ref name="MWR" />，另有一人因踩到断裂的电缆触电身亡<ref name="TB1">{{cite news | agency = [[合众国际社|United Press International]] | newspaper = The Bulletin | date = 1987-09-23 | accessdate = 2016-10-05 | title = Emily regaining strength after hitting Dominican | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=pINTAAAAIBAJ&sjid=p4YDAAAAIBAJ&dq=emily%20evacuations&pg=4712%2C5755887}}</ref>，风暴过后，估计该国有5000人流离失所<ref name="PR4" />。气旋在多米尼加共和国产生的最高降雨量为117毫米<ref name="PG8">{{cite report | author = Harold P. Gerrish | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1987-11-12 | accessdate = 2016-10-05 | title = Hurricane Emily Preliminary Report: Page Eight | format = GIF | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303203203/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1987-prelim/emily/prelim08.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1987-prelim/emily/prelim08.gif | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-03 }}</ref>，该国农业受灾特别严重，损失数额达3000万美元<ref name="PR4">{{cite report | author = Harold P. Gerrish | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1987-11-12 | accessdate = 2016-10-05 | title = Hurricane Emily Preliminary Report: Page 4 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | format = GIF | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303223012/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1987-prelim/emily/prelim04.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1987-prelim/emily/prelim04.gif }}</ref>。艾米莉过去后，该国有数以百计的志愿者协助政府官员清理灾区，并向疏散到避难所的灾民伸出援手。[[国际红十字与红新月运动|红十字会]]同样向当地派出支援，援助无家可归的灾民<ref name="TB1" />。整场飓风一共造成三人死亡，经济损失达8030万美元<ref name="MWR" /><ref name="PR4" />。

艾米莉在[[海地|海地]]上空经过，但没有造成重大破坏和人员丧生，这主要是因为该国山区的森林覆盖率还比较高，估计达到原有水平的四分之一。相比之下，这些森林到2004年时已经只剩下1.4%。<ref>{{cite web | author = Jane Deren | publisher = Saint Bridget Church | year = 2008 | accessdate = 2012-02-22 | title = Hurricanes and Haiti: A Tragic History | url = http://saintbridgetchurch.org/haitihurricanes_08.pdf | format = PDF | archivedate = 2012-02-22 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120222205200/http://www.saintbridgetchurch.org/haitihurricanes_08.pdf }}</ref>此外，风暴还在巴哈马产生时速95公里的大风，最高降雨量34毫米<ref name="PG8" />。

气象部门起初估计，艾米莉即便经过百慕大，风速也不会太强，结果岛上居民被时速达150公里的狂风杀了个措手不及。汽车和船只所受影响最大，还有部分房屋同样在风暴经过期间受到重创。飓风在该岛共计造成5000万美元损失，幸而无人遇难。时速超过180公里的阵风导致16人受伤，约有230幢建筑的屋顶被掀。当地机场关闭，楼房的大片屋顶被吹飞。许多汽车和船只被气旋掀翻，还有一艘载有700人的游轮从系泊处脱离。<ref>{{cite news | agency = Associated Press | newspaper = The New York Times | date = 1987-09-26 | title = Hurricane in Bermuda Causes Minor Injuries | url = http://www.nytimes.com/1987/09/26/world/hurricane-in-bermuda-causes-minor-injuries.html | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160217060907/http://www.nytimes.com/1987/09/26/world/hurricane-in-bermuda-causes-minor-injuries.html | publisher = The New York Times Company | archivedate = 2016-02-17 | accessdate = 2016-10-05 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | newspaper = ''[[华盛顿邮报|The Washington Post]]'' | date = 1987-09-26 | accessdate = 2016-10-05 | title = Hurricane Emily Buffets Bermuda | url = http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-1345289.html | archivedate = 2012-10-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121025223731/http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-1345289.html | deadurl = yes }}</ref>风暴登陆前，百慕大政府官员切断岛上九成地区的供电，保护电网安全<ref>{{cite news | agency = Associated Press | newspaper = The Boston Globe | date = 1987-09-26 | accessdate = 2016-10-05 | title = Hurricane injures 16 in Bermuda | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121025223747/http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-8029279.html | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-8029279.html | archivedate = 2012-10-25 }}</ref>。此外，还有报导称艾米莉催生出多场[[龙卷风|龙卷风]]，但这些消息没有得到证实。艾米莉是[[1948年大西洋飓风季|1948年]]后袭击百慕大的最强飓风。<ref name="MWR" />

